## App Logic documentation
- `.appLogic/`: Core application specification directory
  - Contains markdown files defining:
    - Application architecture
    - Business logic flows
    - Component interactions
    - Data models and relationships
    - API specifications
    - Business rules and requirements
  
  Purpose:
  - Serves as the source of truth for implementation
  - Provides reference documentation for the AI agent
  - Maintains consistency across development
  
  Usage Rules:
  - Read-only reference during normal operation
  - Modifications only upon explicit user request
  - Changes here impact overall application behavior

